window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Dive into the world of ChatGPT and Prompt Engineering: A Comprehensive Guide</b></p> <p><i>Artificial intelligence surrounds us, and ChatGPT stands at the forefront.</i></p> <p>Launched in November 2022, ChatGPT swiftly moved from simple Q&amp;A to reshaping businesses and lifestyles. Its 100 million users showcase its lasting impact and utility.</p> <p>This book is your key to leveraging ChatGPT effectively. Whether for career advancement, business enhancement, or personal growth, it provides actionable insights and strategies.</p> <ul> <li><b>Over 50 ways ChatGPT enhances productivity and creativity</b></li> <li><b>Essential prompt engineering techniques and applications</b></li> <li>Understanding AI's role in society and its potential</li> <li>The US.E. Method for adapting to AI-driven changes</li> <li><b>Why ChatGPT won't replace your unique skills and talents</b></li> </ul> <p><i>And much more!</i></p> <p>Embrace the future with confidence. This book demystifies ChatGPT, guiding you to not just survive but thrive in an AI-centric world.</p> <p><b>Ready to explore the potential of ChatGPT? Click “Add to Cart” and start your journey!</b></p>"; 
